    <item>
      <title>日元因日本央行举措而下跌，欧洲股指期货上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/asian-stocks-set-to-fall-yen-steady-ahead-of-boj-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受中国和香港股市下跌的影响，亚洲股市下跌，而由于日本央行推迟就其债券购买计划做出决定，日元兑美元汇率下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/asian-stocks-set-to-fall-yen-steady-ahead-of-boj-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 22:34:14 GMT</pubDate>
